        Database design, compliance, privacy policies, Internet of Things    







I am a Ph.D. student in Professor Sharad Mehrotra's group at the University of California, Irvine. My research interests lie in database design with a focus on designing for compliance to data regulations like GDPR, CCPA, etc., security, and privacy policies. For more information, please visit my website vishalc.com.

 







